{"title":"收获二题","authors":["巴波"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获二题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁掠空秋风紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背驮蓝天热汗横；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手攥庄稼镰挥动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀光闪闪迎风鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少心血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少历程；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经多少风风雨雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经多少闪电雷鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管天管地管世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治山治水惊鬼神；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕夏锄忙三秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水浇出好年成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割一把庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了伟大祖国繁荣昌盛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割一把庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了全世界反帝斗争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割一把庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为胜利加一把劲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割一把庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命尽一份心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！那熟透了的庄稼啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使割地人心里热气腾腾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三秋即景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼撂倒了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地成了彩色锦缎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片紫红、土黄、棕褐……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从平地铺上岗地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从岗地铺上了天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！又一个丰收到人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一车车满载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声声响鞭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天天往来不息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条道路起尘烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声不断飞向白云间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！送公粮人人争先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步步迈的实在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵?喝震山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股股泥土的浪花翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天的地里沸腾象春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老贫农的心劲高万丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！要把大地全犁遍。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}